## Key policies (summary)

| Policy | Details | Full reference |
|--------|---------|----------------|
| **Zero-copy** | Original synthesis only; no copy-paste from textbooks/institution samples | [01_educational-content-rules.mdc](./01_educational-content-rules.mdc) |
| **Source material** | Internal, read-only, never reference in public docs | [06_source_material_rules.mdc](./06_source_material_rules.mdc) |
| **Voice** | Swamy's first-person learning journey; avoid instructor/course framing | `.github/copilot-instructions.md` |
| **Code style** | PEP 8, `pathlib`, comments explain *why* | `.github/copilot-instructions.md` |
| **Notebooks** | Context → Data setup → Cleaning/transformation → Validation → Reflection | [03_quality-assurance.mdc](./03_quality-assurance.mdc) |

